div.div: Add a one-line explanation of what this file represents

div.p: The Flag of the Philippines with a light blue shade, replacing the former navy blue and superseded by the current royal blue. Adopted by the government of Ferdinand E. Marcos in the last years of the Fourth Republic (1985-1986).
